#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:1
msgid "Support collaboration among CAVEs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:3
msgid ""
"The RenderingParallel module now provides support for synchronizing "
"collections of actors among the synchronized renderers.  The first such "
"supported actor type is vtkOpenGLAvatar, which lays the foundation for "
"supporting collaboration among users of HMD-based VR and CAVEs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:5
msgid ""
"To add a new type of synchronizable actor in the future, you can simply "
"subclass vtkSynchronizableActors and implement the four api methods:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:7
msgid "InitializeRenderer"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:8
msgid "CleanUpRenderer"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:9
msgid "SaveToStream"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:10
msgid "RestoreFromStream"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:12
msgid ""
"And then update vtkSynchronizedRenderers::EnableSynchronizableActors to "
"instantiate your new class."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:14
msgid "Other minor improvements supporting collaboration in CAVEs include:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:16
msgid ""
"vtkFlagpoleLabel now supports CAVEs by making the label face the camera eye "
"point (rather than the desktop camera position) when in off-axis projection "
"mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:17
msgid ""
"vtkVRCollaborationClient now allows customizing the default initial avatar "
"up vector from the new default of [0, 1, 0]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:18
msgid ""
"vtkVRCollaborationClient now allows specifying an arbitrary object as the "
"source of Move3DEvents used to share local pose with collaborators"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/hmd-cave-collaboration.md:19
msgid ""
"vtkOpenGLAvatar now provides api access to get the associated avatar label"
msgstr ""
